OL,6,FA stalker who hid a a tracking device
OL,7,Fin a child's pram to follow a woman in
OL,8,FMansfield has been sentenced.
OL,10,FThe victim contacted Nottinghamshire
OL,11,FPolice to report she was being tracked
OL,12,Fby Mirian Picrri after he turned up at
OL,13,Fseveral locations she had visited in
OL,14,FMarch of this year.
OL,16,FThe 30-year-old was arrested at
OL,17,FMansfield Park on 27 March police
OL,18,Fseized his phone.
