OL,3,CStalker hid tracking device in pram of
OL,4,Cvictim's son
OL,6,FAn application on his phone raised
OL,7,Fsuspicions and Nottinghamshire Police
OL,8,Fwere able to confirm a device was
OL,9,Fbeing tracked.
OL,11,FAfter the woman was contacted,
OL,12,Fofficers were able to track her using
OL,13,FPicrri's phone as she returned to the
OL,14,Fpolice station.
OL,16,FA spokesperson said: "This led us to
OL,17,Fbelieve there was some form of
OL,18,Ftracking device hidden in her son's
OL,19,Fpushchair.
