OL,3,CStalker hid tracking device in pram of
OL,4,Cvictim's son
OL,6,F"We searched the pram, with the
OL,7,Fvictim's consent, and used the
OL,8,Foffender's phone to activate a sound
OL,9,Foption on the tracker.
OL,11,F"We heard a faint ringing coming from
OL,12,Fthe pram as we continued our search
OL,13,Fand eventually found and seized the
OL,14,Fsmall tracking device which was linked
OL,15,Fto the offender's phone."
OL,17,FPicrri, who also persistently called
OL,18,Fthe victim, admitted stalking.
